.Dd $Mdocdate: September 07 2023 $
.Dt C_UINT_64PACK 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm c_uint_64pack
.Nd store unsigned little-endian 64-bit integer
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb tertium
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In tertium/cpu.h
.In tertium/std.h
.Ft char *
.Fn c_uint_64pack "char *s" "u64 u"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn c_uint_64pack
function portably stores the 64-bit integer
.Fa u
to
.Fa s
in little-endian byte order.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The
.Fn c_uint_64pack
function returns a pointer to the given buffer.
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bd -literal -offset indent
char buf[sizeof(u64)];
c_uint_64pack(buf, 31);
.Ed
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr c_uint_64bigpack 3
